## Query


We can use either the openEO process `query_stac` or another method to select input products for processing with FORCE. See the [next section](query.qmd) for an in depth discussion on the different methods how inputs may be specified.


:::{.callout-note collapse="true" title="query_stac process definition"}

::: {#fc6319b2 .cell execution_count=3}
``` {.python .cell-code}
